; Coverage test for amount.cc line 1223
; "Incorrect use of decimal comma" error
; With --decimal-comma, periods are thousands separators.
; If a comma appears after a period has already been seen,
; and the comma comes with an improper placement, error is raised.

2024/01/01 Bad format
    Expenses:Food       1,000.500 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test bal --decimal-comma -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 8:
While parsing posting:
  Expenses:Food       1,000.500 EUR
                      ^^^^^^^^^^^^^
Error: Too many commas in amount
end test
